Take your time.

191
00:10:38,019 --> 00:10:40,065
Is that him?

192
00:10:43,110 --> 00:10:45,736
From the moving company.
He was here today.

193
00:10:45,736 --> 00:10:48,047
And is he the man you saw

194
00:10:48,047 --> 00:10:49,337
