605
00:39:14,085 --> 00:39:18,029
Not like my good Faith at all.

606
00:40:01,251 --> 00:40:03,619
Shouldn't be calling ex-cons.

607
00:40:04,577 --> 00:40:07,848
You're lucky you got me and, uh...

608
00:40:07,848 --> 00:40:10,001
not Andre.

609
00:40:10,001 --> 00:40:12,667
That was you on the phone?

610
00:40:12,667 --> 00:40:15,170
You don't call men

611
00:40:15,170 --> 00:40:18,188
